Mohammad Ali Akhtar was attacked by a knife-wielding robber at Premier Stores in Flixton . 
  The man stormed in brandishing a large kitchen knife and demanded all the money from the till . 
  The shopkeeper was stabbed in the ear and hand and has revealed he thought he was going to die . 
  He was only on his second shift at the store when he was attacked . 
  CCTV footage shows the man wrestle with the shopkeeper before fleeing empty handed . 
 